  "fun_fact": "Lactitol has a double life - it's both a food sweetener AND a prescription medicine! At low doses it sweetens your sugar-free chocolate, but at higher doses it's sold as a laxative to treat constipation. It also acts as a prebiotic, feeding good gut bacteria!"
